POIN Proc_RadianceDamage RadianceHeal RadianceMarking
POIN Post_Nightcaller DawnPendantPostBattle AftershockPostBattle DawnEye
POIN Canto CantoPlus TryProcMoveStar HypeTrainPost Alacrity//this order for canto and friends is the only one I tested ; Canto (put here to test mount universal canto) - loog
POIN PostCombatIncrementFatigue PostCombatStaffIncrementFatigue
